Class AeQueuingReplyReceiver

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.reply.AeReplyReceiverBase

All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeReplyReceiver
Direct Known Subclasses:
AeDurableQueuingReplyReceiver
public class AeQueuingReplyReceiver
extends AeReplyReceiverBase

Provides a way of passing the outcome of the invocation back into the engine by queuing the message data or the fault (instead of calling notifyAll).
